      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON CHANT (3) could not have been more impressive a few runs back in her speedy 22.66 win at this track over 400m then has finished in the placings in both runs since. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. BUSTING (2) made light work of a wide draw last time with a slick early sectional but gathered in and had to settle for the minors, finishing third (22.99) at this track over 400m. Goes very well from this draw with two wins and two minor placings from four starts. Bold showing expected. PRETTY PANAMA (6) has hit the frame here at the last two runs, most recently finishing second beaten 1.75 lengths (22.81). Can measure up. BIG MAKO (4) must be respected at his pet track and distance.",
